flowchart LR
    A([Application]) --> B[Create UDP socket\nsocket SOCK_DGRAM]
    B --> C[sendto: dest IP + port\n+ datagram payload]
    C --> D[OS: Add UDP header\nSrc port, Dst port,\nLength, Checksum]
    D --> E[OS: Add IP header\nSrc IP, Dst IP,\nTTL, Protocol=17]
    E --> F{NAT Device?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Rewrite src IP:port\nRecord mapping]
    G --> H[Network Transit\nRoute via IP]
    F -->|No| H
    H --> I{Packet Lost?}
    I -->|Yes| J([Datagram dropped\nNo retransmission])
    I -->|No| K[Destination receives\nIP+UDP packet]
    K --> L[Strip IP header\nVerify checksum]
    L --> M[Deliver to app\nvia dest port]
    M --> N([Application receives\ndatagram — no ACK sent])
